    "description": "JANOME Corporation engages in the planning, development, and production of sewing machines in Japan, North America, Europe, Oceania, Central and South America, the rest of Asia, and the Middle East. The company offers home appliances, such as embroidery/sewing, sewing, professional sewing, overlock, and professional embroidery. It also provides industrial equipment, such as servo presses, desktop, and cartesian robots, as well as automatic screw presenters and die casting products. In addition, the company develops systems, constructs software, and outsources system operations control. The company was formerly known as Janome Sewing Machine Co., Ltd. and changed its name to JANOME Corporation in October 2021. JANOME Corporation was founded in 1921 and is headquartered in Hachioji, Japan."
